---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Experience | Pouria Alaei"
  description="Professional experience of Pouria Alaei in embedded systems, Embedded Linux, Edge AI, and hardware/software integration."
>
  <main class="page">
    <section class="section intro">
      <p class="eyebrow">Experience</p>
      <h1>Embedded engineering experience across real products.</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        My experience combines embedded software, hardware/software integration,
        system architecture, industrial devices, and technical leadership.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="timeline">
      <article class="card item">
        <p class="date">Current</p>
        <h2>Senior Embedded Software Engineer / Technical Lead</h2>
        <p>
          Leading and contributing to embedded systems projects involving
          Embedded Linux, Qt HMI, device networking, backend services,
          hardware/software integration, and production-oriented system design.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card item">
        <p class="date">Previous</p>
        <h2>Embedded Systems Engineer</h2>
        <p>
          Designed and developed firmware, hardware interfaces, communication
          modules, Linux-based device software, and industrial control features
          for connected embedded products.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card item">
        <p class="date">Technical Strengths</p>
        <h2>Hardware + Software Integration</h2>
        <p>
          Experienced in debugging real hardware, integrating communication
          modules, validating system behavior, and connecting low-level embedded
          design with user-facing software and backend services.
        </p>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .eyebrow {
    color: #67e8f9;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  h1 {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 12px 0 0;
    font-size: clamp(42px, 7vw, 72px);
    line-height: 1.05;
  }

  .lead {
    max-width: 760px;
    color: #cbd5e1;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .timeline {
    display: grid;
    gap: 18px;
    padding-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .date {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    color: #67e8f9;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0;
    color: #93c5fd;
  }

  p {
    color: #cbd5e1;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
</style>
